Class TLFunctionLibrary

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.ctl.extensions.TLFunctionLibrary
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITLFunctionLibrary
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContainerLib, ConvertLib, DateLib, DynamicLib, IntegralLib, MathLib, RandomLib, StringLib, TLFunctionLibraryExt, UtilLib

    public abstract class TLFunctionLibrary
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITLFunctionLibrary
    Recommended ascendant of all TL function libraries. This class is intended to be subclassed by function libraries defined in external engine plugins.
